OL,3,CCurlers land back in the UK following
OL,4,COlympic effort
OL,6,FSouth of Scotland curlers returned
OL,7,Fhome with a silver medal following the
OL,8,F2026 Milano Cortina Winter Olympics.
OL,10,FThe men's team landed in London fresh
OL,11,Ffrom from their medal on Saturday,
OL,12,FGrant Hardie, Bobbie Lammie and Hammy
OL,13,FMcMillan Jr were part of squad, who
OL,14,Fnarrowly missed out on gold to Canada.
OL,16,FLed by their Skip, Bruce Mouat, the
OL,17,Fquartet were opening to clinch a gold
OL,18,Fthis year after also taking home a
OL,19,Fsilver from 2022 Winter Olympics.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
