CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1772062271
OL,3,CCurlers land back in the UK following
OL,4,COlympic effort
OL,6,FHardie and Lammie are both from
OL,7,FDumfries with McMillan Jr being born
OL,8,Fin Stranraer, making the South of
OL,9,FScotland one a key part of Team GB's
OL,10,Fsuccess this year.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News at Gatwick
OL,13,FAirport, Bobby Lammie said: "It is
OL,14,Famazing, we didn't expect to see as
OL,15,Fmany people here.
OL,17,F"They were making some good noise for
OL,18,Fus as well so it has been a cool
OL,19,Freception walking through the doors to
OL,20,Fthat. It puts a cap on quite a
OL,21,Fmemorable couple of weeks."
OL,26,@uD@]OU
