OL,3,CCurlers land back in the UK following
OL,4,COlympic effort
OL,6,FIt's been two weeks of last two weeks
OL,7,Faction in Italy, reflecting on this,
OL,8,FGrant Hardie said: "It is amazing
OL,9,Fbecause we know that platform only
OL,10,Fcomes once every four years.
OL,12,F"To try and showcase our sport in the
OL,13,Fbest possible way we can getting to
OL,14,Fthe final gives us the best
OL,15,Fopportunity to do that.
OL,17,F"The final itself was a great game of
OL,18,Fcurling and showed how good a sport
OL,19,Fcurling is."
OL,26,@pD@TOU
