OL,3,CCurlers land back in the UK following
OL,4,COlympic effort
OL,6,FIt was a different set of fortunes for
OL,7,Fthe women's side, who at the Beijing
OL,8,Fgames four years ago the side had won
OL,9,Fgold, but this success was not to be
OL,10,Frepeated in Milan.
OL,12,FBoth Sophie Jackson and Fay Henderson
OL,13,Ffrom Dumfries made up part of the
OL,14,Fsquad for ladies curling team, they
OL,15,Fjust missed out on qualifying for the
OL,16,Fsemi finals.
OL,18,FThey flew home today without medals
OL,19,Fcoming sixth overall.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
