OL,3,CCurlers land back in the UK following
OL,4,COlympic effort
OL,6,FIn the mixed doubles Team GB missed on
OL,7,Fbronze coming fourth, although there
OL,8,Fwas no representation from the South
OL,9,Fof Scotland.
